responsivePhotos.caption: This well-maintained and clean studio condo is perfect for 1-2 people.
Enjoy watching your favorite shows on this Samsung 46" TV.
Murphy bed with Queen-size mattress. New linens and quilt!
Futon sofa converts to a full-size bed. Glass-top adjustable height desk with office chair.
Luxury vinyl plank flooring.
Iron, ironing board, fire extinguisher, broom, dust pan, vacuum and swiffer.
Closet organizer with 5 shelves and 3 hanging racks. Extra 3-drawer organizer provided.
Dead bolt, sliding door lock and 24/7 building security guards for your safety. The building also has a smoke alarm and sprinkler system, and a voice evacuation system was recently installed.
Stacked GE washer/dryer. Shared coin-operated washers and dryers are also available on the 2nd floor. Car wash area is on the ground floor.
Kitchen is newly renovated.
Spoons, forks, steak knives, etc.
Dishes, bowls, coffee mugs, water glasses, wine glasses, sauce bowls, measuring cup and plastic storage containers with lids.
Toaster, kettle and rice cooker for your use.
Pots, pans, bowl, serving tray, colander, spatula, slotted spoon, etc. to help with your cooking needs.
Bathroom is newly renovated.
New bathroom cabinet and medicine cabinet. Bath towels and beach towels provided.
Cleaning supplies and toilet paper provided to start you off.
Nice view of the city while you're cooking.
Large windows provide natural lighting during the day.
University of Hawaii is about half a mile from the condo. HPU is approx 3 miles away. Chaminade University is 1.5 miles away. Three Biki bike stations and bus stops are a short walk from the condo.
Distance from condo to: Kaimana Beach, Waikiki (~3 miles) Ala Moana Shopping Center (~1 mile) Kahala Mall (~3.5 miles) Downtown Honolulu (~3.5 miles)
If you're lucky, you'll wake up to a gorgeous double-rainbow outside your window!
Two tennis courts
Swimming pool and jacuzzi in enclosed area.
Spacious recreation deck with swimming pool, jacuzzi, sauna room, tennis courts, putting green, BBQ area and recreation room on the 5th floor.
BBQ grills
Air conditioned recreation room which can be reserved for parties. Refrigerator/freezer and stove/range available for your party use.
